desc: Source directly from the LU Ranch we provide the highest quality grass-fed, grass-finished beef. Our products are currently Beef Jerky, Beef Sticks, Ground Beef, and dry-aged well marbled steaks.

layout.text: Your source for well marbled, grass-fed and finished beef. All of our cattle are born and raised on the LU Ranch in Hot Springs County, WY and processed in Cody, WY at Wyoming Legacy Meats.
